此得到独到的见解，深受听者喜爱。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p></section></section></section><section style="white-space: normal; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 667px; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 3px 3px 0px 0px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(162, 138, 92); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">书单介绍</strong></p></section><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appWawLB9IH1520/image/ueditor/43030600_1545124462.png" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 0.8em; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section><section style="width: 667px; font-size: 0px; margin-top: -2px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 667px; margin-right: -6px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; margin-top: -2px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border: 1px solid transpare